body.description: Manufactured by the #1 leading manufacturer of First Aid Kits in the USA. The Be Smart Get Prepared 110 Pieces First Aid Kit meets the United States FDA Regulatory Standards as a Medical Device. Ideal for most businesses and perfect for family use at home or travel. manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our Mission To be the most dependable and excitingly innovative manufacturer of First Aid Kits, Emergency Preparedness Kits in all categories of Home, Office, School, Auto, Sporting Goods, Outdoors, Marine and Farm for the purpose of spreading the good news, supporting Ministries and Missionaries of all nations, in their calling and election to care for orphans, help the poor, and feed the hungry, shelter the homeless, encourage, comfort and urge everyone to live lives worthy of God. Be Smart Get Prepared What started out as a small family-owned business in 1991, Total Resources International (TRI) grew to become the most reliable manufacturer of First Aid Kits and Emergency Preparedness Essentials in the nation. For over 29 years, we have worked hard to develop, manufacture and distribute premium products and services that provide smart, sensible solutions under the Be Smart Get Prepared brand. By embracing research, trends, practicality, functionality and innovative technology, our products address consumer needs, help secure personal and family safety, and promote overall wellness. Be Smart Get Prepared products can be found in Health & Beauty, Outdoors, Auto, Sporting Goods, and Industrial Hardware sections in mass market and specialty retail stores all over the nation.
Our Commitment We design with you in mind and are committed to providing excellent service and creating quality products that offer smart, sensible solutions.

reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars It's ok, very affordable and small
reviews.reviewText: I haven't tested the bandages for adhesion yet. I plan on keeping this kit in a trunk in case of emergencies.I removed 1 star as the sterile packages have no manufacturing or expiration dates.This price is extremely affordable. I wish more antibiotic ointment came with this kit.Cons: No expiration dates. Tongue depressors are junk,l and not even individually wrapped. Gloves are loose in the package I will add my own sterile gloves to the kit.
